Simple NoSQL order management system.

API is described in the file orders.thrift

To produce API documentation and SDKs for variety of languages issue the command: "make all". See Makefile for the details of the targets.

About thrift: https://thrift.apache.org/

Server code is located in the Server sub-folder. SSL protection: using stunnel.

Client examples: look at the ClientExamples sub-folder.

